OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold start to the morning,
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and a scattering of
OL,7,Fshowers. Showers becoming largely
OL,8,Fconfined to the far west and east of
OL,9,Fthe UK by the afternoon, but some
OL,10,Fheavy and thundery. Chilly, with
OL,11,Ftemperatures below average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowery rain moving eastwards
OL,14,Facross northern Scotland. Elsewhere,
OL,15,Fmostly dry with clear spells but a few
OL,16,Fshowers still possible in the west. A
OL,17,Flight frost possible in the
OL,18,Fcountryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
