OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FBreezy across the northwest,
OL,6,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain. Drier
OL,7,Ffurther south and east, with sunny
OL,8,Fspells and a few showers. Feeling a
OL,9,Flittle warmer in the south.
